'Name' => '名稱',
'Name examples: Demand response, Empty email, Reminder. Basically the same as Message Type' => '名稱示例：需求響應，空電子郵件，提醒。基本上與消息類型相同',
'Name2' => '名稱2',
'No, I can\'t come and do this task' => '不，我不能來做這個任務',
'Note that the column headers can be clicked on to sort the list by that column in ascending or descending order.' => '請注意，可以單擊列標題以按列升序或降序對列表進行排序。',
'Notifications' => '通知',
'Notify this user of event problems' => '通知此用戶事件問題',
'One very important setting here is the \'always notify\' field for each member of the team. If this is set to true then that person will receive all the notifications that come to the team from the event manager. If you want you can have all the members of the team receive these notifications. But at least you would want the team leader to have this set to true.' => '這裡一個非常重要的設置是團隊中每個成員的“始終通知”字段。如果將此設置為true，則該人員將從事件管理器接收來自團隊的所有通知。如果您願意，您可以讓團隊的所有成員都收到這些通知。但至少你會希望團隊領導者將此設置為真。',
'Only fill in this if \'Use an automatically created subject\' is false (not checked). This will then be the subject of the email.' => '如果“使用自動創建的主題”為false（未選中），則僅填寫此內容。這將是電子郵件的主題。',
'Only fill this in if \'Show Accept Button\' is true. In that case you must enter some positive text.' => '如果“顯示接受按鈕”為真，則僅填寫此內容。在這種情況下，您必須輸入一些正文。',
'Only fill this in if \'Show Link To Object\' is true. Write something that shows that this is a link to the event' => '如果“Show Link To Object”為true，則僅填寫此內容。寫一些東西，表明這是一個事件的鏈接',
'Only fill this in if \'Show Reject Button\' is true. In that case you must enter some text showing a negative response.' => '如果“顯示拒絕按鈕”為真，則僅填寫此內容。在這種情況下，您必須輸入一些顯示否定回复的文本。',
