'See and edit their own profile.' => '查看和編輯自己的個人資料。',
'See own task list and reject/accept tasks.' => '查看自己的任務列表並拒絕/接受任務。',
'See teams and team task lists that they are associated with.' => '查看與其關聯的團隊和團隊任務列表。',
'See the events.' => '查看活動。',
'Setup' => '建立',
'Several churches can share the same installation yet they will see nothing of each others information' => '幾個教會可以共享相同的安裝，但他們不會看到彼此的信息',
'Share files at all levels.' => '在各個級別共享文件。',
'Show Accept Button' => '顯示接受按鈕',
'Show Link To Object' => '顯示鏈接到對象',
'Show Reject Button' => '顯示拒絕按鈕',
'Simply put a name here describing what the message is about. For example: Demand response, Empty email, Reminder' => '只需在此處輸入一個名稱來描述消息的內容。例如：需求響應，空電子郵件，提醒',
'Smartphone' => '手機',
'Song' => '歌曲',
'Song attachement' => '宋附庸',
'Song database with CSV and OpenLP import and CSV export.' => '具有CSV和OpenLP導入和CSV導出的Song數據庫。',
'Songs are a central part of many worship services. Here also they have a central role. There are usually so many songs that it is unreasonable to type in them all by hand. That is why you have the CSV import and the OpenLP import.' => '歌曲是許多崇拜服務的核心部分。他們在這裡也發揮著核心作用。通常有這麼多的歌曲，手動輸入它們是不合理的。這就是您進行CSV導入和OpenLP導入的原因。',
'Special needs' => '特殊需求',
'Status' => '狀態',
'Subject' => '學科',
'Table of contents' => '目錄',
'Task templates' => '任務模板',
'Tasks' => '任務',
'Tasks are easy to define with a multitude of possibilities' => '任務很容易定義，具有多種可能性',
'Tasks may also be accepted or rejected by the user inside of the program instead of by email.' => '用戶也可以在程序內部而不是通過電子郵件接受或拒絕任務。',
'Team' => '球隊',
'Team Manager' => '團隊經理',
'Team Type' => '團隊類型',
'Team association. People can be organized into teams when desired.' => '團隊協會。可以根據需要將人員組織成團隊。',
'Team members' => '團隊成員',
'Team type examples: Prayer team, Hosting team, Usher team, Praise and psalm team' => '團隊類型示例：禱告團隊，託管團隊，亞瑟團隊，讚美和詩篇團隊',
'Teams' => '小組',
'The CSV import is usually simple enough for many people to succeed. But still you need to do it right. The best way to do a CSV import is to first write one song in by hand into the database. Then export that to a CSV file to see how it looks. Use that as a template for how to import all your songs with CSV.' => 'CSV導入通常很簡單，許多人都可以成功。但你仍然需要做得對。執行CSV導入的最佳方法是首先手動將一首歌寫入數據庫。然後將其導出到CSV文件以查看其外觀。使用它作為模板，了解如何使用CSV導入所有歌曲。',
'The ISO Name is very important that you get it exactly right. Several directories are to be named the exact same name.' => 'ISO名稱非常重要，您可以完全正確地使用它。幾個目錄的名稱完全相同。',
'The OpenLP import is much easier. The OpenLP format uses one XML file for each song. Zip together all the songs you have exported from OpenLP into one zip file without any subdirectories. Then do the OpenLP import with that ZIP file.' => 'OpenLP導入更容易。 OpenLP格式為每首歌使用一個XML文件。將從OpenLP導出的所有歌曲壓縮到一個沒有任何子目錄的zip文件中。然後使用該ZIP文件執行OpenLP導入。',
'The author of the song. Of course there are authors and music composers and translators. Somehow you need to fit all of these into this field.' => '這首歌的作者。當然還有作家和音樂作曲家和翻譯。不知何故，你需要將所有這些都融入這個領域。',
'The church screen is only for the most advanced users. This screen is to manage multiple churches in the same database.  Normally, you will only have one church in one database and then this screen is unnecessary. However, you might see the need for a test church where people can come in and test using \'WorshipHHN\'. Here you could create such a church or any other church if that is needed.' => '教堂屏幕僅適用於最高級用戶。此屏幕用於管理同一數據庫中的多個教會。通常，您只在一個數據庫中擁有一個教堂，然後不需要此屏幕。但是，您可能會看到需要一個測試教會，人們可以使用\'WorshipHHN\'進入並測試。如果需要，你可以在這裡創建這樣的教堂或任何其他教堂。',
'The definition of the role you can find in the concepts documentation. It is to large to put here.' => '您可以在概念文檔中找到角色的定義。放在這裡很大。',
'The envelope icon beside each name allows you to send a predefined email to that person. If you don\'t see that envelope icon it is because you don\'t have permissions to do that. There is also a button to send a predefined email to all the persons in this list.' => '每個名稱旁邊的信封圖標允許您向該人發送預定義的電子郵件。如果您沒有看到該信封圖標，那是因為您沒有權限這樣做。還有一個按鈕可以向此列表中的所有人發送預定義的電子郵件。',
'The event orgainizer will recieve an email notification anytime a task is rejected by a user.' => '只要用戶拒絕任務，事件orgainizer就會收到電子郵件通知。',
'The event task list is easy to read and exportable in PDF or EXCEL format.' => '事件任務列表易於閱讀並可以PDF或EXCEL格式導出。',
'The following is the list of roles and their meaning. This is a heirarchical list where each time you go up a level you inherit all the permissions of the lower levels. This list is shown from the lowest to the highest level' => '以下是角色列表及其含義。這是一個層次列表，每次上升一級時，您都會繼承較低級別的所有權限。此列表顯示從最低級別到最高級別',
'The language you wish to view in all the menus and screens' => '您希望在所有菜單和屏幕中查看的語言',
'The messages you define here may or may not require the user to respond by pressing a button that is in the email they receive. There is a lot of flexability in these message definitions.' => '您在此處定義的消息可能需要或可能不需要用戶通過按下他們收到的電子郵件中的按鈕進行響應。這些消息定義中有很多靈活性。',
'The most important challange here is finding your event. There is a filter to aid in finding the event but this filter is shown as a button. Click on the icon to the right of the filter button and then the filter will open up and you can specify exactly what dates you are interested in seeing. If you hit the button \'clean\' then you will empty the data fields. Then when you hit filter you will get all the defined events. By default you will see only events from today and 3 months forward in time.' => '這裡最重要的挑戰是找到你的活動。有一個過濾器可幫助查找事件，但此過濾器顯示為按鈕。單擊過濾器按鈕右側的圖標，然後過濾器將打開，您可以準確指定您有興趣看到的日期。如果按“清除”按鈕，則會清空數據字段。然後，當您點擊過濾器時，您將獲得所有已定義的事件。默認情況下，您只會看到今天和3個月前的事件。',
'The most important challange here is finding your task. There is a filter to aid in finding the task but this filter is shown as a button. Click on the icon to the right of the filter button and then the filter will open up and you can specify exactly what dates you are interested in seeing. If you hit the button \'clean\' then you will empty the data fields. Then when you hit filter you will get all the defined tasks. By default you will see only tasks from today and 3 months forward in time.' => '這裡最重要的挑戰是找到你的任務。有一個過濾器可幫助查找任務，但此過濾器顯示為按鈕。單擊過濾器按鈕右側的圖標，然後過濾器將打開，您可以準確指定您有興趣看到的日期。如果按“清除”按鈕，則會清空數據字段。然後，當您點擊過濾器時，您將獲得所有已定義的任務。默認情況下，您只能看到今天和3個月前的任務。',
'The name of the song. The name that the song is most known by. This data field together with the author is a unique identifier for the record. It is with these two fields an import knows whether to update or add the song.' => '這首歌的名字。這首歌最為人所知的名字。該數據字段與作者一起是記錄的唯一標識符。在這兩個字段中，導入知道是否更新或添加歌曲。',
'The task lists can also be exported to PDF or EXCEL format.' => '任務列表也可以導出為PDF或EXCEL格式。',
'The task lists can be directly transfered over to your own personal calendar.' => '任務列表可以直接轉移到您自己的個人日曆。',
'The valid email for the user. It is possible to put here a fake email in the case that your user will probably never log into the system and you don\'t need to have any communications with them.' => '用戶的有效電子郵件。如果您的用戶可能永遠不會登錄系統並且您不需要與他們進行任何通信，則可以在此處放置一封虛假的電子郵件。',
'This is a completely translated system at all levels. To achieve this you must define here the languages that you will be using. Probably you have recieved a lot of languages installed when you first installed the system. Feel free to delete any languages you are sure you don\'t want.' => '這是一個完全翻譯的系統。要實現此目的，您必須在此定義您將使用的語言。您可能在第一次安裝系統時收到了許多安裝的語言。隨意刪除您確定不需要的任何語言。',
'This is a person who has verified his email but not yet been given any permissions at all. This role has no permissions' => '這是一個已經驗證了他的電子郵件但尚未獲得任何權限的人。此角色沒有權限',
'This is an abstraction level in the messaging system that allows you to group together identical message templates that are in different languages. The goal of this grouping is so that a person may get the message in the language that they prefer. Of course, most implementations of this program will only be in one language so that this abstraction level is only an irritation and doesn\'t offer any new functionality.' => '這是消息傳遞系統中的抽象級別，允許您將不同語言的相同消息模板組合在一起。這種分組的目的是讓一個人可以用他們喜歡的語言來獲取信息。當然，該程序的大多數實現只能使用一種語言，因此這種抽象級別只是一種煩惱而且不提供任何新功能。',
'This is mainly for the service organizer task.' => '這主要是針對服務組織者的任務。',
'This is only a single name input. Nothing else. The group name.' => '這只是一個單一的名稱輸入。沒有其他的。組名。',
'This is the abstraction that allows the language independence. If you define two or more message templates with the same message type and different languages then you have the ability to send one or the other depending on which language your user prefers.' => '這是允許語言獨立的抽象。如果您定義兩個或多個具有相同消息類型和不同語言的消息模板，則可以根據用戶喜歡的語言發送一個或另一個。',
'This is the body of the email and you must always put something here.  If you want this message to be completely blank to only show the custom message then put something here like a period.' => '這是電子郵件的正文，你必須總是在這裡放一些東西。如果您希望此消息完全空白以僅顯示自定義消息，則在此處添加類似句點的內容。',
'This is the heart of all configuration for \'WorshipHHN\'. Therefore it is important that you spend time here to make your event management correct. Here is where the contents of all tasks are defined but not the tasks themselves.' => '這是\'WorshipHHN\'所有配置的核心。因此，您必須花時間在這裡使事件管理正確。這是定義所有任務的內容而不是任務本身的位置。',
'This is the main screen where everything happens. This one screen is the goal of the entire program. Here you see all the tasks which must be done to ensure a successful event.' => '這是一切都在發生的主屏幕。這一個屏幕是整個計劃的目標。在這裡，您可以看到為確保事件成功而必須完成的所有任務。',
'This is the song itself. For some installations this could be left blank because only the name is needed in this program. But others may feel the need to put the entire song here because many songs are very similar and also for searching purposes. In the create and update screens this text box has a tab in one corner you can pull on to make the text box as big as you want. Otherwise the text box is very small.' => '這就是歌曲本身。對於某些安裝，可以將其留空，因為此程序中只需要名稱。但是其他人可能覺得有必要將整首歌放在這裡，因為許多歌曲非常相似，也用於搜索目的。在創建和更新屏幕中，此文本框在一個角落中有一個選項卡，您可以將其拉出以使文本框盡可能大。否則文本框非常小。',
'This is very similar to a description however it is more for comunicating specific needs for the task.' => '這與描述非常相似，但更多的是用於傳達任務的特定需求。',
'This is where you edit the name of the event and the start and end time of the event. That is all. The main editing is always done by clicking on the task icon' => '您可以在此處編輯事件的名稱以及事件的開始和結束時間。就這些。主要編輯始終通過單擊任務圖標完成',
'This is where you edit the name of the team and the team type.' => '您可以在此處編輯團隊名稱和團隊類型。',
'This is where you edit the profile of the user.' => '您可以在此處編輯用戶的個人資料。',
'This must be set to true if the task is not defined for a specific time slot.' => '如果未為特定時間段定義任務，則必須將其設置為true。',
'This name is only for the user to be able to quickly recognize which message this is about?' => '此名稱僅供用戶快速識別這是什麼消息？',
'This screen allows you to find the event plan you need to see or edit. Plus there are many different aspects of the event you can go to from this screen.' => '通過此屏幕，您可以查找需要查看或編輯的活動計劃。此外，您可以從此屏幕進入事件的許多不同方面。',
'This screen shows you all the tasks you are scheduled to do in the near future.' => '此屏幕顯示您計劃在不久的將來執行的所有任務。',
'This screen shows your team all the tasks you are scheduled to do in the near future.' => '此屏幕向您的團隊顯示您計劃在不久的將來執行的所有任務。',
'This will take you to the file sharing area for the specific event. However, inside of the event you can attach files to individual tasks. Here is for putting files that you can\'t find a specific task to attach to.' => '這將帶您進入特定事件的文件共享區域。但是，在事件內部，您可以將文件附加到各個任務。這是用於放置您無法找到要附加的特定任務的文件。',
'This will take you to the file sharing area for the team.' => '這將帶您進入團隊的文件共享區域。',
'Unavailability' => '不可用',
'Under the \'menu\' column you can see up to five icons depending on what your permission level is. Each of these icons will send you to different aspects of the event or perform an action on the event plan. The icons are defined as follows' => '在“菜單”列下，您可以看到最多五個圖標，具體取決於您的權限級別。每個圖標都會將您發送到活動的不同方面或對活動計劃執行操作。圖標定義如下',
'Under the \'menu\' column you can see up to six icons depending on what your permission level is. Each of these icons will send you to different aspects of the event or perform an action on the event plan. The icons are defined as follows' => '在“菜單”列下，您可以看到最多六個圖標，具體取決於您的權限級別。每個圖標都會將您發送到活動的不同方面或對活動計劃執行操作。圖標定義如下',
'Under the \'menu\' column you can see up to six icons depending on what your permission level is. Each of these icons will send you to different aspects of the team or perform an action on the team. The icons are defined as follows' => '在“菜單”列下，您可以看到最多六個圖標，具體取決於您的權限級別。每個圖標都會將您發送到團隊的不同方面或對團隊執行操作。圖標定義如下',
'Under the \'menu\' column you can see up two icons depending on what your permission level is. They are for accepting or rejecting the task. In some installations this might be your primary way of accepting or rejecting tasks. Or it might be done in emails instead. Consult your system administrator to find out how it will be done.' => '在“菜單”列下，您可以看到兩個圖標，具體取決於您的權限級別。它們用於接受或拒絕任務。在某些安裝中，這可能是您接受或拒絕任務的主要方式。或者它可能在電子郵件中完成。請諮詢您的系統管理員，了解如何完成。',
'Use Description' => '使用說明',
'Use Globally (No start time)' => '全球使用（無開始時間）',
'Use Song' => '使用歌曲',
'Use Special Needs' => '使用特殊需求',
'Use Team' => '使用團隊',
'Use User' => '使用用戶',
'Use an automatically created subject' => '使用自動創建的主題',
'Use bible verse' => '使用聖經經文',
'Use file' => '使用文件',
'User' => '用戶',
'User guide' => '用戶指南',
'User images can be shown where ever a users name appears.' => '用戶圖像可以顯示在用戶名出現的位置。',
'Username' => '用戶名',
'Users' => '用戶',
'We think this program is a simple and powerful tool you can use to plan events for your church. We use it to plan all our church services.' => '我們認為這個程序是一個簡單而強大的工具，可用於為教會規劃活動。我們用它來計劃我們所有的教會服務。',
'What language will this message be in? This is an important part of being able to send the same message to different persons in different languages' => '這條消息將以什麼語言出現？這是能夠以不同語言向不同人發送相同消息的重要部分',
'When you have more then one church, you must remember that each church is completely seperate from another church. There is nothing common between the churches. Therefore for each new church you must create everything from the beginning.' => '如果你有一個以上的教會，你必須記住，每個教會都完全獨立於另一個教會。教會之間沒有什麼共同之處。因此，對於每個新教會，你必須從一開始就創造出一切。',
'Will a bible verse need to be defined so others can coordinate the showing of that verse? Or possibly just tell others what bible verses you plan to use.' => '是否需要定義聖經經文以便其他人可以協調該節經文的展示？或者可能只是告訴別人你打算用什麼聖經經文。',
'Will a team be needed or used to do this task?' => '是否需要團隊來完成這項任務？',
'Will a user be needed or used to do this task?' => '是否需要用戶來執行此任務？',
'Will some sort of file be needed to properly define this task?' => '是否需要某種文件來正確定義此任務？',
